    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "August 31, 1966",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "J. E. Hoover, F.B.I. Director",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Wash. D.C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Dear Sir:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "I am a member of \"Nicap\" and am very much",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "interested in U.F.O (Flying Saucers)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Several weeks ago a fellow employee received a letter (business)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "from Arizona with a stamp on the back (see enclosed).",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Being interested in U.F.O's I asked for the stamp & sent 3.00",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "for the 12 issues of AFSCA.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Having received & read my first issue I feel it isnt just",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "what it appears on the surface. I cant say just why, but",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "with my limited idea of how Communists operate it",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "strikes me it is backed by them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "My reason for writing this is that I consider myself a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "true American, I am told my ancestors go back to a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "[unclear] Grandmother who was an Indian Squaw &",
      "status": "needs_image_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "I'm proud of it. If by writing for this AFSCA Report,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "my name could in any way be aligned with the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Communist party, I would like to know if there is any",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "way I can get things straightened out.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "I may be all wrong about my interpretation of this report",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "but I'd like to be sure since I expect I will get the other",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "issues as they come up.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "I will be 63 yrs old in a few days.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "My husband passed away 4-30-65 [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "I have worked [unclear]",
      "status": "needs_image_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Manchester N.H 44 years this month",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Very truly yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
